Test case 1:
LoginWithValidAccount

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
5) Click on "Вход" button

Expected result:
User successfully logged in. User icon and login are displayed in the right-top corner.

Test case 2:
CheckThatUserCannotLogInWithoutPassword

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Click on "Вход" button

Expected result:
User stayed on logIn page

Test case 3:
CheckLogout

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
5) Click on "Вход" button
6) Click on icon in the right-top corner
7) Click on "Выход" button

Expected result:
User is logout and redirect to login page

Test case 4:
CheckResetPassword

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Click on "Напомнить пароль" link

Expected result:
User is redirected to empty page

Test case 5:
CheckCreationOfServiceRecord

Pre-conditions:
1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
3) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
4) Click on "Вход" button
5) In sidebar-menu click on "Словари" -> "Аппарат"
8) Click on "+" button
9) Into "Apparat number" field enter valid number
10) Into "Apparat comment" field enter valid comment
11) In sidebar-menu click on "Словари" -> "Сотрудники"
12) Click on "+" button
13) Into "Worker surname" field enter valid worker surname
14) Into "Worker name" field enter valid worker name
15) Into "Worker middle name" field enter valid worker middle name
16) Into "Worker phone" field enter valid Worker phone name


Steps:
1) In sidebar-menu click on "Обслуживание"
2) Click on "+" button
3) Into "Service changes" field enter valid service changes
4) Into "Service operations" field enter valid service operation
5) From "Service date" select valid date&time
6) From "Аппарат" combobox select valid value
7) From "Сотрудник" combobox select valid value
8) Click on "Создать" button

Expected result:
Record with is created and appears in "Список работ" table

Post-conditions:
1) Click on created record
2) Click on "Удалить" button
